====================================
MBBL -- a bootloader for MicroBlaze.
====================================

Directories:
============

* mbbl-imagetool should be installed in the build environment (see
  README in mb-linux-msli repository).

* mbbl should be compiled along with FPGA configuration using header
  and library files generated by Xilinx tools. makefile.inc contains
  relevant sections from Xilinx Makefile. This version is intended 
  to be placed into BRAM or external RAM.
  See mbbl/mbbl/mbbl/ldscripts/*.ld for target address ranges.


